OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782919119
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FPeople wanting Bayeux Tapestry tickets
OL,7,Fwill have to be patient after more
OL,8,Fthan 55,000 people joined the queue on
OL,9,Fthe British Museum's website.
OL,11,FThe wait time was more than an hour on
OL,12,FWednesday morning, but a message
OL,13,Fadded: "This is the fastest way to
OL,14,Fbook tickets."
OL,16,FThe museum was also flooded with phone
OL,17,Fcalls and emails on the first day of
OL,18,Fticket sales.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
