CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782919119
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FAround 7.5 million people are expected
OL,7,Fto visit as the tapestry returns to UK
OL,8,Fsoil for the first since it was made
OL,9,Falmost 1,000 years ago.
OL,11,FIt is expected to be one of the most
OL,12,Fpopular events in the museum's history.
OL,14,FGeorge Osborne, chairman of trustees
OL,15,Fat the British Museum, described the
OL,16,Ftapestry as a "defining piece of our
OL,17,Fnation's history and a truly once-in-a-
OL,18,Flifetime experience".
OL,26,@xD@OOUzD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
