OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782919119
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FTickets to see the 70 metre-long
OL,7,Ftapestry will first be available for
OL,8,Fentry on dates between September and
OL,9,FDecember.
OL,11,FTwo further ticket releases will be
OL,12,Fmade in October and January for access
OL,13,Fbetween January to March, and April to
OL,14,FJuly 2027.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
