FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782919119
OL,3,CStars show off their gnomes as Chelsea
OL,4,CFlower Show gets under way
OL,6,FFormer Conservative chancellor Mr
OL,7,FOsborne said: "This will be without
OL,8,Fdoubt the biggest year in the museum's
OL,9,Fhistory ` as we expect 7.5 million
OL,10,Fpeople to visit as the Bayeux Tapestry
OL,11,Freturns to UK soil for the first time
OL,12,Fin 1,000 years.
OL,14,F"It is a defining piece of our
OL,15,Fnation's history and a truly once-in-a-
OL,16,Flifetime experience.
OL,18,F"I hope people mark their calendars
OL,19,Fand seize the chance to see it when it
OL,20,Farrives, in what promises to be an
OL,21,Fextraordinary moment for the country."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
